cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the implementation of a decentralized ride-hailing platform using blockchain technology, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR). The platform also involves distributed computing and networking (cs.DC) as well as cybersecurity (cs.CY). The development of the platform requires software engineering practices (cs.SE) and the evaluation of its performance involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
